===Etymology===
From the {{m|ja|未然形|tr=mizenkei||incomplete form}} ''tataka'' of verb {{m|ja|叩く|tr=tataku||to [[strike]]}} + auxiliary verb {{m|ja|ふ|tr=fu|pos=indicating repetitive or ongoing action}} → “to [[strike]] [[repeatedly]]” → “to [[fight]]”.<ref name="KDJ">{{R:Kokugo Dai Jiten}}</ref><ref name="DJR"/><ref name="DJS">{{R:Daijisen}}</ref>

